WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:02.758
<i>Previously on Broadchurch...</i>

00:02.759 --> 00:05.038
Saturday morning, day of the party,

00:05.039 --> 00:08.559
Trish and me,
we were in bed together.

00:08.560 --> 00:12.360
She's my best friend.
If she ever finds out, I'll...

00:12.400 --> 00:15.359
- Is, uh, Daisy in?
- Who are you?

00:15.360 --> 00:17.158
Just tell her the boys came round.

00:17.159 --> 00:20.159
I heard what happened. I thought
maybe you'd need a friend.

00:21.560 --> 00:23.038
What did you find out?

00:23.039 --> 00:24.719
I've got
everything you asked for.

00:24.720 --> 00:26.758
I've found Joe.
Time to put things right.

00:26.759 --> 00:28.238
- We did that.
- We bloody didn't!

00:28.239 --> 00:30.038
Yes, we did!
Enough of this shit, Mark!

00:30.039 --> 00:31.878
I am Danny's dad - I'm not gonna stop

00:31.879 --> 00:33.838
until I know I've done right by him.

00:33.839 --> 00:36.118
Aaron Mayford - three years

00:36.119 --> 00:38.518
for the rape of a woman
at a budget hotel.

00:38.519 --> 00:42.279
His victim was tied and
gagged, just like Trish.

00:42.280 --> 00:44.878
Two years ago,
in a field, walking home.

00:44.879 --> 00:48.158
He tied me up, put a gag in my mouth.

00:48.159 --> 00:52.600
I was raped and I never told anyone.

