35:56.759 --> 35:58.439
but that's not your fault.

36:00.200 --> 36:02.239
Jim slept with Trish.

36:03.680 --> 36:05.438
- What?
- Yeah.

36:05.439 --> 36:08.638
- Jim and Trish?
- Morning of my party.

36:08.639 --> 36:10.359
She wouldn't do that!

36:10.360 --> 36:13.199
Look, I know you think
the sun shines out of her arse,

36:13.200 --> 36:15.478
but she shagged my husband.

36:15.479 --> 36:18.438
Or he shagged...
They shagged each other.

36:18.439 --> 36:19.959
She told me.

36:21.639 --> 36:23.078
What was she thinking of?

36:23.079 --> 36:27.279
My God!

36:27.280 --> 36:29.518
Full marks for being a shitty consoler.

36:29.519 --> 36:31.519
Sorry.

36:32.639 --> 36:34.159
What are you gonna do?

36:36.079 --> 36:37.758
I don't know.

36:37.759 --> 36:41.759
He's had women before,
I know that, but this just...

36:42.879 --> 36:44.400
hurts more.

36:46.319 --> 36:47.878
I get that.

36:47.879 --> 36:51.359
I just thought my life would
be that I'd love someone

36:51.360 --> 36:53.239
and they'd love me back and...

36:55.319 --> 36:57.800
it would last my whole life.

36:59.879 --> 37:01.600
Why's that so much to ask?

37:16.879 --> 37:21.679
Brilliant!

37:21.680 --> 37:24.158
Seriously, mate, that is classic.

37:24.159 --> 37:26.360
Breakdown lorry broken down.

37:27.239 --> 37:29.399
No, don't be an arsehole.

37:29.400 --> 37:31.680
Ugh!

37:33.200 --> 37:35.919
What, you don't want me
to tow it for you then?

37:35.920 --> 37:38.000
Very funny.

37:40.920 --> 37:43.238
Bad about your party, wasn't it?

37:43.239 --> 37:45.079
- Dunno what you mean.
- Don't you?

37:46.119 --> 37:48.158
Can't really believe it, can you?

37:48.159 --> 37:50.919
What some people are capable of.

37:50.920 --> 37:52.719
Yeah, I don't want to talk about it.

37:52.720 --> 37:55.638
It's all anyone's talking about,
soon as they get in the cab.

37:55.639 --> 37:57.479
You're the only one
who doesn't fancy her.

38:00.959 --> 38:02.560
Poor Trish.

38:03.600 --> 38:05.878
How'd you know it was her?

38:05.879 --> 38:08.878
Mate, it's all round the town.

38:08.879 --> 38:11.599
At least they kept her
name out of the papers.

38:11.600 --> 38:13.719
Hard for you and your wife.

38:13.720 --> 38:15.680
Must've been someone you invited.

38:17.039 --> 38:19.280
- Must it?
- Just by logic.

38:20.119 --> 38:22.158
Why are you so interested?

38:22.159 --> 38:25.758
Well, I dropped some people
there and back that night.

38:25.759 --> 38:27.638
Ah, right.

38:27.639 --> 38:30.758
So you were around the place,
but you weren't invited.

38:30.759 --> 38:33.958
Yeah, I see
what you're doing there.

38:33.959 --> 38:35.838
Ah, do you?

38:35.839 --> 38:37.919
Funny, though. I saw you.

38:37.920 --> 38:39.758
With Trish.

38:39.759 --> 38:41.719
I was parked up,
you were out the front,

38:41.720 --> 38:43.438
to the side of the house.

38:43.439 --> 38:46.599
Looked like quite an intense chat.

38:46.600 --> 38:50.158
What are you saying? You were
spying on me at my wife's party?

38:50.159 --> 38:51.999
Not spying, mate, just saw.

38:52.000 --> 38:54.279
Ah, you just saw two friends talking.

38:54.280 --> 38:56.799
Uh, it looked a bit more than that.

38:56.800 --> 38:59.279
- Pull over.
- What?

38:59.280 --> 39:02.280
I said pull over
before I smack you hard.

39:14.439 --> 39:16.639
Listen, I don't want any trouble.

39:19.159 --> 39:21.158
Do you know who you're talking to, hmm?

39:21.159 --> 39:23.958
Do you know how many people
I know in this town?

39:23.959 --> 39:25.799
Not really.

39:25.800 --> 39:28.638
I know your boss,
I know your colleagues

39:28.639 --> 39:30.318
and I know your customers.

39:30.319 --> 39:33.279
I can find out about your wife,
your kids, your pets.

39:33.280 --> 39:35.920
And I can very easily make your life

39:35.959 --> 39:38.439
much more of a misery
than it must already be.

39:40.400 --> 39:43.239
- Right.
- Right.

40:39.920 --> 40:42.478
<i>You have one new message.</i>

40:42.479 --> 40:44.638
<i>Mark, it's me.</i>

40:44.639 --> 40:48.720
<i>Can you call me, please?
I'm worried about you.</i>

40:51.239 --> 40:53.800
<i>Message deleted.</i>

41:16.879 --> 41:18.599
Trish Winterman is attacked here.

41:18.600 --> 41:19.999
Attack on Laura Benson here.

41:20.000 --> 41:22.038
And then a third in Budmouth, here.

41:22.039 --> 41:25.518
So one on private
land, one in an open field

41:25.519 --> 41:27.719
and the other on the edge of a town.

41:27.720 --> 41:30.318
All quite obscure areas, I suppose.

41:30.319 --> 41:32.838
You'd only tend to go to
those places deliberately,

41:32.839 --> 41:34.279
which might suggest someone local.

41:34.280 --> 41:36.238
Aye, it might, but we're
clutching at straws.

41:36.239 --> 41:38.078
We are a bit.

41:38.079 --> 41:40.599
How about we cross-reference those areas

41:40.600 --> 41:43.799
with the addresses of all
the guests at the Atwood party?

41:43.800 --> 41:45.319
OK. We'll give it a go.

41:47.000 --> 41:48.559
Thank you.

41:48.560 --> 41:50.119
- For coming here.
- That's fine.

41:50.159 --> 41:52.118
Can have a word with her if you like.

41:52.119 --> 41:54.559
- Think it would help?
- I don't know. Your daughter.

41:54.560 --> 41:58.559
I just feel like I'm failing
at everything, Miller.

41:58.560 --> 41:59.999
That's parenting.

42:00.000 --> 42:02.280
It's like one constant
slap around the head.

42:03.360 --> 42:06.719
Oh, wait. Wait, what if
it's not geographical?

42:06.720 --> 42:08.399
- What if it's seasonal?
- What?

42:08.400 --> 42:10.118
All the attacks happened
in the summer months.

42:10.119 --> 42:12.199
Two in June, one right
at the end of May.

42:12.200 --> 42:14.879
There isn't a link in where
but there is a link in when.

42:14.920 --> 42:16.518
That'd point to someone
not here all year.

42:16.519 --> 42:18.559
Yeah - seasonal worker,
returning tourist.

42:18.560 --> 42:20.958
No, 'cause how does that connect
to the people at the party?

42:20.959 --> 42:23.399
- They're all mates, all live round here.
- God, I don't know.

42:23.400 --> 42:25.399
That doesn't narrow it down,
Miller, that makes it wider.

42:25.400 --> 42:27.279
I'm doing the best I can,
following the information.

42:27.280 --> 42:28.958
All we need is one name.

42:28.959 --> 42:30.200
Just one hit.

42:32.280 --> 42:33.719
What?

42:33.720 --> 42:35.118
It's Arthur Tamworth

42:35.119 --> 42:36.800
from Axehampton House.

42:36.839 --> 42:38.999
I was given this number to call.

42:39.000 --> 42:42.078
Only, I don't know whether my dog

42:42.079 --> 42:44.239
might have found something pertinent.

43:12.839 --> 43:14.518
Closed.

43:14.519 --> 43:16.680
Are you deaf? I said we're closed.

44:02.360 --> 44:04.719
I just noticed Pedro
had it in his mouth.

44:04.720 --> 44:07.279
No idea where he found it
or how long he'd had it.

44:07.280 --> 44:09.559
I thought I should call you,

44:09.560 --> 44:12.438
even though it is just an old sock.

44:12.439 --> 44:15.199
One never knows in your
line of work, I suppose.

44:15.200 --> 44:17.079
Quite.

44:25.239 --> 44:26.838
Right, lads. Let's call it.

44:26.839 --> 44:28.758
Let's get your bibs in the bag.

44:28.759 --> 44:31.118
Kits to me when you're changed.

44:31.119 --> 44:33.919
My turn to wash again.

44:33.920 --> 44:37.159
Unless I can get a lucky
lady to do it for me.

